headline: DIGITIMES Asia Tech Forum 2025: Qualcomm and MediaTek take smartphone rivalry to the cloud in AI chips
summary: With global smartphone sales leveling off, Qualcomm and MediaTek are taking their long-running rivalry into the fast-growing cloud AI ASIC market. DIGITIMES Research estimates MediaTek controlled 37% of the smartphone application processor market in 2024, ahead of Qualcomm at 27%. Together, the two suppliers accounted for more than 60% of shipments.
